<div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 20px;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif">
  <h1 style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:8px">Help Center</h1>
  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#555;margin-bottom:32px">Find answers to common questions and get support for your orders.</p>

  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:40px">
    <a href="/pages/tracking" style="text-decoration:none;padding:24px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;display:block">
      <div style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:8px">📦</div>
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:4px">Track Your Order</h3>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666">Enter your order number and email to see real-time tracking updates.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/policies/refund-policy" style="text-decoration:none;padding:24px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;display:block">
      <div style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:8px">↩️</div>
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:4px">Returns & Refunds</h3>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666">Learn about our return policy and how to initiate a return.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/policies/shipping-policy" style="text-decoration:none;padding:24px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;display:block">
      <div style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:8px">🚚</div>
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:4px">Shipping Info</h3>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666">Delivery times, shipping costs, and international shipping details.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/pages/contact" style="text-decoration:none;padding:24px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;display:block">
      <div style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:8px">💬</div>
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:4px">Contact Support</h3>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666">Can't find what you need? Our team is ready to help 24/7.</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:16px">Common Topics</h2>

  <div style="border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:16px">
    <details style="padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0">
      <summary style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#333;cursor:pointer">My order hasn't arrived yet</summary>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:10px">First, check your tracking number on our <a href="/pages/tracking" style="color:#e53e3e">tracking page</a>. Delivery times vary by source: Amazon (3-7 days), AliExpress/SHEIN (7-20 days), Macy's/Sephora (5-10 days). If the estimated date has passed, contact us.</p>
    </details>
    <details style="padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0">
      <summary style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#333;cursor:pointer">I received a damaged item</summary>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:10px">We're sorry about that. Please <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:#e53e3e">contact us</a> within 48 hours with photos of the damage. We'll arrange a replacement or full refund.</p>
    </details>
    <details style="padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0">
      <summary style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#333;cursor:pointer">How do I return a product?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:10px">Sign in to your account, go to your order, and click "Return items." Follow the prompts to select items and reason. You can also <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:#e53e3e">contact us</a> for help with your return.</p>
    </details>
    <details style="padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0">
      <summary style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#333;cursor:pointer">I need to change my shipping address</summary>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:10px">If your order hasn't shipped, contact us immediately and we'll update the address. If it's already shipped, we may not be able to change it. Check your order status first.</p>
    </details>
    <details style="padding:16px 20px">
      <summary style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#333;cursor:pointer">Where is my refund?</summary>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-top:10px">Refunds are processed within 3-5 business days after we receive and inspect the returned item. The refund will appear on your original payment method. Bank processing may take an additional 5-10 days.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align:center;padding:32px;background:#f8f9fc;border-radius:12px;margin-top:32px">
    <h3 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:8px">Need more help?</h3>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666;margin-bottom:16px">Check our <a href="/pages/faq" style="color:#e53e3e">full FAQ</a> or contact our support team.</p>
    <a href="/pages/contact" style="display:inline-block;background:#e53e3e;color:#fff;padding:12px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none">Contact Support</a>
  </div>
</div>

